betterwallpaper (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Setup Wizard for first-run configuration
  * Scheduler for automatic wallpaper changes
  * Slideshow mode with configurable intervals
  * Profile system for saving wallpaper configurations
  * Theme integration (color extraction)
  * Advanced transitions with multiple effects
  * Native wallpaper setter support (swaybg, hyprpaper, swww)
  * Resource monitoring with automatic fallback
  * Smart audio mute based on window focus
  * Error dialogs and crash recovery
  * Steam Workshop integration with error handling
  * Fuzzy search for tags
  * Favorites view with empty state

 -- Onxy <onxy@example.com>  Fri, 31 Jan 2026 10:00:00 +0100
